snippet.title: Birth of Mewtwo - Amber's Death - English Fandub
snippet.description:
This is just a quick re-audition to see if Darkshadedx will have me as a part for the Pokemon Radio Drama: Myuutsuu no Tanjou.
I was asked to lower Mewtwo's voice a bit, and I think I did that. I did the part where Amber starts to die. ; 3; That part always makes me cry, no matter how many times I've heard it
